\lim _{x \to \infty}\sum_{1}^{\infty}\frac{x^2}{1+n^2x^2}=\sum_{1}^{\infty}\frac{1}{n^2}
x^2
x \to \infty
    \frac{1}{n^2} \frac{x^2}{1+x^2} \leqslant \frac{1}{n^2} \frac{x^2}{x^2 + n^{-2}} < \frac{1}{n^2} 
     \frac{x^2}{1+x^2} \sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{1}{n^2} \leqslant \sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{x^2}{n^2+x^2} < \sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{1}{n^2} 
 \sum \left( \frac{1}{n^2} - \frac{x^2}{1+n^2x^2} \right) = \sum \frac{ 1}{n^2(1+n^2 x^2) }  \leq \frac{1}{x^2} \sum \frac{1}{n^4} \to 0.
